          <li class="pkg-feature"><span class="pkg-check">✓</span>FlowEngine custom automations</li>
          <li class="pkg-feature"><span class="pkg-check">✓</span>Full marketing system + content calendar</li>
          <li class="pkg-feature"><span class="pkg-check">✓</span>PocketOps mobile AI agent</li>
          <li class="pkg-feature"><span class="pkg-check">✓</span>Omni-channel AI (voice + chat + SMS)</li>
